    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, r u saying i actually need the ER?? i'm really scared of hospitals and i don't have much money. is it really that serious? i feel like i can almost walk it off if i just get the pain under control. i have some leftover strong stuff in my cabinet, can i just take a double dose of that so i can sleep through the night? it's probably just something i ate.",
